\noindent
Confirmed tutors: Fernando Perez, Stefan van der Walt, Jarrod Millman, Matthew
 Brett, Caterina Gratton (UC Berkeley), Ariel Rokem and Jonathan Taylor
 (Stanford), Michael Hanke (University of Magdeburg), Yaroslav Halchenko
 (Dartmouth College), Gael Varoquax (INSERM), Alex Gramfort (MGH/Harvard),
 Eleftherios Garyfallidis (Cambridge), Satrajit Ghosh (MIT), Chris Filo
 Gorgolewski (University of Edinburgh), Stephan Gerhard (ETH Zurich).
\end_layout

